author: Sally Rose
title: PwC M&A guru Alex Cameron loses bid for The Bachelorette
text:
PwC M&A adviser Alex Cameron has his bid for Sam Frost's heart rejected on Channel 10 reality dating show The Bachelorette. Courtesy Channel 10 "I absolutely still believe in love, meeting Sam will re-energise that for me. Fingers crossed love is just around the corner".
The smooth-talking Englishman was not available to speak to the media on Friday. It is understood he is lying low visiting family in the UK, leaving his colleagues on the PwC deals team to bat off all those awkward questions about whether or not the beanie-wearing baldie has started dating someone since the show wrapped filming.
One can only guess what Cameron's clients - among them notoriously media shy private equity firms such as Bain Capital and Pacific Equity Partners - make of his very public "journey".
PwC dealmaker Alex Cameron gave the The Bachelorette Sam Frost a surfing lesson before he got wiped out of the Channel 10 reality dating show. Courtesy Channel 10
